scene.message:
Butterfly: Young one.{nl}
Within Iwato, you two{nl}
will be alone.{nl}
Are you fully prepared?{waitkey}Are your weapons and{nl}
items in order?{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: Very well.{nl}
I shall open the path to{nl}
the Sea of Consciousness.{nl}
It lies behind the shrine.{waitkey}Go forth.{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: Do you wish to go{nl}
elsewhere? Then rejoin{nl}
your companions.{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: If you mean to go{nl}
outside, don't forget to{nl}
rejoin your companions.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: We'll be waiting{nl}
right here.{nl}
Don't push yourself.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
just 'cause you're alone with{nl}
Sonomura, don't go losing{nl}
your self-control!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: N-nothing, right,{nl}
{ctl0f:1}?{nl}
Heh heh, just guy talk.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: That sounds kinda dirty.{nl}
Oh well.{nl}
{ctl07:1}, hurry, hurry!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Stay alert.{nl}
There's no telling{nl}
what's in there.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Where are you going?{nl}
Well, no matter, but{nl}
we haven't much time.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I'm happy, you know...{nl}
Because I'm not alone...{nl}
because everyone, and{nl}
you, are here... right!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...I'd like to have{nl}
it out with you sometime.{nl}
Don't go dying on me.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Where are you going?{nl}
I'll follow you anywhere{nl}
you go, {ctl07:1}...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Where are you going?{nl}
I'll accompany you anywhere{nl}
you go, {ctl07:1}...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1}...{nl}
do be careful...{nl}
I'll be waiting...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1}...{nl}
please be careful...{nl}
I'll be waiting...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Oh? Not going yet?{nl}
Heh-heh, I bet you're{nl}
getting cold feet?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
you're still not going?{nl}
Don't tell me you're scared?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl08:65281}Still not going?{nl}
Don't tell me{nl}
you're scared?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
make sure you go and{nl}
see Sonomura, okay!{waitkey}{ret}
